    "en": {
      "title": "Wikileaks exposed Ranil",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "WikiLeaks has exposed the actions taken by the current President Ranil Wickremesinghe in 2007 when he was in office as the Leader of the Opposition.",
        "The WikiLeaks website has exposed that Ranil Wickremesinghe had asked Japan to stop providing financial aid to Sri Lanka.",
        "It is mentioned in WikiLeaks that Japan has rejected Ranil Wickramasinghe's request and said that Japan should not punish the people of Sri Lanka for the mistakes made by the leaders."
      ],
